Working on an offseason swerve drive, and I was wondering if the 6th entry in the 0 to Autonomous series’s code was still valid(well, valid after updating to 2023) to base a swerve drive from. I really liked their explanation of everything and the code seemed simpler than a lot of the other swerve solutions out there. Github of the code i’m talking about is linked below. Thanks in advance!
